  // ===== ORGAN H2 · THREE TARGETS (DEPTH BUILD WAVE 2): goals intake as a worksheet — ceiling 3 / floor 1; each target = an area + ONE next brick + WOOP armor; planted as journey quest-lines (S.goals). Ends on the ACTION-stamp law (a 10-second body act). =====
